    "7326401": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Babel",
        "Step": "Babel seems to have something urgent to talk to you about...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Esteemed Master of the Jinni! There is an urgent matter that I need to inform you of!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "I was so shocked when I first heard about it... Oh, where should I begin..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Jeht... Jeht, she's... I hate to say it, but she... could very well be a traitor to the tribe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do you have any proof?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Some time earlier, we caught a northerner who knew Jeht. He told us... that Jeht had revealed to them the location of all our outposts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "If all our outposts are exposed, the actions of the entire Tanit tribe in the desert will be utterly restrained..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "What's more, according to him, Jeht has already sent out several batches of assassins, her very target being you... who possesses the Jinni."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!? Isn't that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Ahem!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "If his confession's true, Jeht should be active in their camp."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "And according to our recent reports, the northerners are indeed closing in on our tribe. They have bypassed our sentries and set up camps at a dangerously close distance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Those are signs, not proof."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "In the desert, no one should take any ominous sign lightly. The excessive speculation of \"Jeht is a traitor\" is just the worst inference I have made based on the existing signs..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Plus... She hasn't been back for a long time. I'm really worried about her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Please forgive me for making such a speculation... But I genuinely think of her as my own daughter. No matter what she might've become, it is the consequence of my own mistake..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Therefore, esteemed Master of the Jinni, I beg you, regardless of the path she has chosen, bring her back to me..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Whether she lives to prove her innocence, or has paid for her missteps."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Tell me where she might be."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... did Jeht really betray us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "I'll mark the location of the northerners' forward operating base on your map. Just keep looking in this direction and you won't miss it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I will find her, figure everything out, and bring her back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Sorry, it all happened so suddenly... It's hard even for me to accept such a twist."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Please bring her back to me and let me talk to her, will you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Don't worry. We will!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
