    "7326402": {
        "Desc": "Enter the Fatui outpost",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "H—H—Hello, e—e—esteemed Master of the Jinni!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How have things been lately?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "N—Not too bad. It was quite a shame that we lost Aderfi, a—along with all those goods. Fortunately, we still have contact with o—other merchants, so the l—loss is s—still acceptable."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Th—The supply of seeds, soil, and Anahitian Blessing is fairly normal, b—but some annoying bandits s—s—still show up every now and then and rob our caravans. D—Darn it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Traitors, and Jeht... Ugh! Must be those northerners behind all this!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About Jeht..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "I—I—I'm sorry... I never thought sh—sh—she would become a traitor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Matriarch Babel trusted her so much. I—I—I adored her as well. She was like a l—little an—antelope, hehe... But that northerner said, he said..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Sh—She may be coming for you. If you are to investigate the matter, please d—do be careful!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Th—The assault last time... Sh—She must've been the one who's behind it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "*sigh* H—How, how could this happen..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the northerners..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Th—They came into the desert a long time ago. Th—They'd trade things with us, teach us new te—te—techniques."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "At that time, w—we thought they were good people, much warmer than those city people who live in trees..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "But then, th—they started using those advanced, shiny things to lure our people, make them b—break away from the tribe, and m—make them rebels."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "Th—That's when we discovered that these northerners a—are not good people, b—but enemies that should be guarded against."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "F—First it was Aderfi and Azariq, now even Jeht..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yuften",
                    "T": "*sigh* Sometimes, I—I—I don't even know who to trust."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7326403": {
        "Desc": "Defeat the Fatui",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Investigate",
                    "T": "Hmm... \"Gerardo,\" \"Ice Cream,\" \"Pierogi\"... They have mixed passwords from different times! Which one's the real password?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Guess we have to try them one by one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Investigate",
                    "T": "Yeah... Paimon has no better idea."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Investigate",
                    "T": "And it looks like they've moved the location of their main camp! Hmm... This map looks way too ugly! Paimon can only roughly make out the direction they went..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Investigate",
                    "T": "Well, let's catch up in the direction they left, shall we?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
