    "7326407": {
        "Desc": "Track down the transferred Fatui",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Who are you? Password!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Password! What was the one that we found again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Gerardo.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Huh? \"Gerardo\"? What is that? Sounds like some air freshener brand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Hey, Ilyusha, \"Gerardo\"! Does that ring a bell? I've never heard of it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "\"Gerardo\"? Nah. Is that the brand of the baby powder you use?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Do I look like someone who uses off-brand baby powder? The Mr. Charming Yevgraf, using \"Gerardo\"!? Am I a joke to you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "C'mon, I was just asking! Why are you so worked up!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "How dare you humiliate me and ask me to calm down? Am I someone with such bad taste? Do I look like someone who uses \"Gerardo\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "*sigh* Alright, sorry! I apologize, come on! Stop fighting over some baby powder! Anyway, what did you just ask...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "Hold on a sec... Yes, you asked about the password! Ah, I do have a vague impression. Lemme check the password list real quick..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Hmph, this is the attitude that my colleague should have!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Hey, you there! Do I look like someone who uses \"Gerardo\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "See, I told you! I only use Fontaine brands. And listen, if you are looking to buy any skin care or hair products, my advice is all you're gonna need."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Don't get yourself fooled by that stupid \"Gerardo.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "Hey, hey, Yevgrash, I found it! The password \"Gerardo\" was selected by Captain Zoya. It's... uh... her favorite puppy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Oh! Oh... I—I see."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "I—I've never used \"Gerardo,\" actually."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "I know, I'll keep it a secret."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Thanks, man."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "But... Well... This password has expired, now that we just changed it. Now it's... Well, it's a little embarrassing, haha. It's that... little... thing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "What? Captain Zoya's cat?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "Pfft... Ahem! N—No. It's another cute little animal. As soft and furry as a cat, but smaller and more docile..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I guess it's bigger than a mouse, but smaller than a ferret."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, what are you doing!? This isn't the time for riddles! We still have business to do!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "That's right! And we, too, have serious work on our hands! Sorry, that was the correct password, but unfortunately, it's no longer valid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "Ding ding ding! You're out! Both of you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "Then what was Captain Zoya's order again? Ah, that's right... Those who fail to match the password shall be executed on the spot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "So, uh, sorry, friend. I can't let others know that I've used \"Gerardo.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ilyusha",
                    "T": "Yeah, we're really sorry... Wait... What do you mean you've used it!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Shut up and fire!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Ice Cream\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Uh... Nope."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Um... \"Pierogi\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Nice try. What next? \"Cheese\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*sigh*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Never mind. Let's just fight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yevgraf",
                    "T": "Uh... Thanks."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, you've actually got manners!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
