    "7322512": {
        "Desc": "Look for Jeht",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "*cough*... Look upon us... The Tanit... ruined... by a single traitor..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "My... tribe... my kin... my Eternal Oasis..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Say goodbye to them, while you still have time for some final words."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Why! ...I once... loved you so much... Why did you... betray me... and the Tanit..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Why? Because you're evil and I'm not. I see no reason why I must explain myself to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "*sigh* Alright... Babel, let me tell you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#It's because {NICKNAME} is {M#my best friend.}{F#my best friend!}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#You wanted to get rid of {M#him}{F#her}, but I refused to be part of it, and so you decided to get rid of me too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "No, you're more despicable than that... You wanted to pit us against each other!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Only then did I realize that you are no \"Prophetess,\" nor do you deserve to be favored by the Queen of All Oases."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You're just a despicable schemer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "You're... the foolish one... *cough* An outsider... You did all this, for an outsider!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "I... We're your real family! You've destroyed everything. You destroyed... the hopes of the Tanit... the hopes of all the tribes who wander... amidst the gilded sands!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Stop bigging yourself up. I just pushed your tiny sand dune over, that's all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#Really, I'm the one with the questions here! What kind of mother would force her daughter to kill {M#her friend}{F#someone she cherishes}, anyway? Answer me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Some family you are — you tried to take my life! Abyss take your idiotic dream of being a prophetess. Well, someone might fulfill it in your stead... But I'm sure they'll keep their hands cleaner than you did."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Haha... Hahaha... But I've already sent scouts to inform all the tribes of... your betrayal..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "Soon, it'll be known... that you're a traitor who tarnished her family's name... *cough*... all across the vast desert... Very soon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "No one will ever accept you again... Never again... will you find a safe place to lay your head..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...When did you do that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "*cough*...! Haha... Right before... you came back..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So you've always wanted us dead, then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But you said before that you wanted to give me a chance to repent... Was that also a lie?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Babel",
                    "T": "I thought... you'd soften... it'd make it easier to get rid of you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You disgust me. All of you."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
