    "7322514": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Jeht",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "So, she set the trap up long ago, and was just waiting for us to walk right into it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Wait... Why didn't you... show me this earlier?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We would've, but you didn't give us a chance to speak before drawing your weapons, and you wouldn't listen to reason either!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Um... *sigh* I'm sorry. Thank goodness you're alright..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Regardless, I have to get to the bottom of this. I need answers from her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Ugh... Ow, ow..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We still have time. You should rest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yup yup, there's no need to rush it. We can return any time, while Babel has to wait for us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon's right. The initiative is on our side now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{M#Mm, you're right. I'm sorry that I didn't trust you...}{F#The initiative, huh...? Hmm...}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, Jeht, show us your wounds already. We'll help bandage you up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "My wounds? Where? Pfft... That's right. They're everywhere! ...Seriously though, I can keep going."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't try to downplay it. Let us have a look."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#{M#*sigh*... Okay. Sorry...}{F#Mm... Okay...}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "And so, you all decide to rest briefly and start a campfire..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "#{M#After carefully tending to Jeht's wounds, you get some rest together with her by the campfire.\\nThough no words are spoken, you both know what must happen next.}{F#After carefully tending to Jeht's wound, you get some rest together with her by the campfire...\\nJeht sleeps peacefully by your side. The mixed odors of blood, sweat, and burning poplar branches cannot fully mask the scent of spices she carries.\\nLight snoring and raving nonsense intertwine in her dreams — she must truly be tired.\\nEven without speaking to one another, you both know what must happen once she awakes.}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...Let's go. Let's find Babel and have her explain everything to us."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
