    "7322511": {
        "Desc": "Part ways with Jeht",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You can always trust us, Jeht!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I know... It's just that I'm left with nowhere to return to again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But put another way, you're now free to call anywhere you wish home."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Pfft, if it were me back then, I'd have thought that you were mocking me! *sigh* But you're right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You're right... Now, I'm the head of my own house."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I'm no longer a servant bound by the name \"Tanit.\" I'm now the master of the name \"Jeht.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I've reclaimed my mother's name... I'm free. Perhaps \"Jeht\" will also become the name of a new clan someday... Maybe? I dunno."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "My mother's name gives me pride, and my father's name also holds many memories for me. As long as I remember them, even in this barren desert... Will that not be the home I was seeking all along?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Now, \"home\" need not be a cause of anxiety for you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Uh... You know what? Actually, I'd love to go on more adventures with you... Haha, never mind that. You must've had enough of me after all the dangerous situations I put you in..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But... I can tell that you have your own journey ahead, a travail of greater solitude and a far grander objective, both of which are beyond what I can bear or imagine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "As for me, I've also set myself on a certain path. You've seen it already... It's not gonna be a peaceful one. And I won't drag you down with me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...C'mon, Jeht, you're not \"dragging us down\" or anything..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Anyway, if you ever feel tired or want to take a breather... I believe that our paths will converge one day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "At that time, I might even invite you to go on a crazy adventure with me again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Phew... I've done enough talking... It's time to leave. There's nothing left here but heartbreak."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "#{M#You hug Jeht before parting ways with her in the desert.\\nShe holds you tightly, and you notice that she seems to be holding back sobs...\\nHowever, she quickly draws back and rubs her wet eyes before smiling broadly at you once more.}{F#You hug Jeht before parting ways with her in the desert.\\nShe holds you tightly, almost as if afraid that a blinding sandstorm would sweep you away. You notice that she seems to be holding back sobs...\\nThen she pushes you away lightly and rubs her wet eyes before smiling broadly at you once more.}"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "\"May we meet again under a lovelier sun,\" she says."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Jeht turns away and leaves.\\nYou see Benben, only now emerging out of the ruined camp, hurry to catch up with Jeht."
                }
            ]
        ]
    }
